--[[
    LucidLib  —  premium Roblox UI library

    Identity: "lucid".  Warm plum-charcoal surface (never flat black), a single
    ember-pink accent, and one animated orange→pink→violet gradient reserved for
    the lowercase wordmark.  Switch toggles (no keybinds), a floating dropdown
    that never reflows the page, clean slide-in notifications, uppercase section
    labels.  No image assets.

    Window controls:  minimize = hide (reopen with the toggle key) · fullscreen ·
    close = fully unload.

    Layout rules (verified in-engine):
      • ClipsDescendants clips to a RECTANGLE not the UICorner — one flat surface,
        never a coloured square panel against a rounded corner.
      • UIStroke (Border) draws OUTWARD and is sliced by a parent's clip — scroll
        columns and the slider track stay padded away from the clip edge.
      • The `×` (U+00D7) glyph renders; `✕` (U+2715) is a tofu box — use ×.

    ── QUICK START ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
      local Lib = loadstring(readfile("LucidLib.luau"))()
      local Win = Lib:Window({ Title="lucid", Key=Enum.KeyCode.RightShift })
      local Tab = Win:Tab({ Title="Combat" })
      local Sub = Tab:SubTab({ Title="Aura" })
      local Sec = Sub:Section({ Side="Left", Title="Auto Attack" })
      Sec:Toggle  ({ Name="Aura", Flag="Aura", Default=false, Callback=function(v) end })
      Sec:Dropdown({ Name="Mode", Flag="Mode", Options={"A","B"}, Default="A", Callback=function(v) end })
      Sec:Slider  ({ Name="Range", Flag="Range", Min=1, Max=20, Default=9, Decimals=1, Callback=function(v) end })
      Sec:Stepper ({ Name="Count", Flag="Count", Min=1, Max=10, Default=5, Callback=function(v) end })
      Sec:Button  ({ Name="Go", Callback=function() end }); Sec:Label({ Text="hi" }); Sec:Divider()
      -- Win:Notify("t","s") ; local cfg=Win:GetConfig() ; Win:LoadConfig(cfg)
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
--]]

